1. 零温且 $\Delta\to0^+$ 时的能隙方程：
$$\frac{1}{g_c} \;=\;\mathcal{N}\int_{|\mathbf k|\le\Lambda_k}\frac{d^3k}{(2\pi)^3}\,\frac{1}{\sqrt{(\hbar v_F k)^2+\Delta^2}}
\;\xrightarrow{\Delta\to0}\;\mathcal{N}\int_{|\mathbf k|\le\Lambda_k}\frac{d^3k}{(2\pi)^3}\,\frac{1}{\hbar v_F\,k}.$$  
2. 切换到球坐标系：
$$\int_{|\mathbf k|\le\Lambda_k}\frac{d^3k}{k}
=4\pi\int_0^{\Lambda_k}\frac{k^2\,dk}{k}
=4\pi\int_0^{\Lambda_k}k\,dk
=2\pi\,\Lambda_k^2.$$  
3. 因此
$$\frac{1}{g_c}
=\mathcal{N}\,\frac{1}{\hbar v_F}\,
\frac{2\pi\,\Lambda_k^2}{(2\pi)^3}
=\frac{\mathcal{N}\,\Lambda_k^2}{4\pi^2\,\hbar v_F}.$$  
4. 当 $\mathcal{N}=2$ 时，
$$g_c=\frac{4\pi^2\,\hbar v_F}{\mathcal{N}\,\Lambda_k^2}
=\frac{2\pi^2\,\hbar v_F}{\Lambda_k^2}\,. $$
